74
00:02:55,309 --> 00:02:56,642
                YOU'RE RIGHT.   

75
00:02:56,644 --> 00:02:58,877
              BUT JUST BECAUSE  
    PERIDOT HASN'T BEEN HERE YET

76
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,679
