167
00:07:07,461 --> 00:07:08,693
        AAH!                    

168
00:07:27,114 --> 00:07:28,747
         [ SCREECHING ]         

169
00:07:28,749 --> 00:07:30,415
     [ PANTING ]                

170
00:07:30,417 --> 00:07:31,550
      MNH-MNH.                  

171
00:07:31,552 --> 00:07:32,717
                       GARNET?  

172
00:07:32,719 --> 00:07:34,419
                   UH...GARNET! 

173
00:07:34,421 --> 00:07:35,987
               WHAT DO WE DO?!  

174
00:07:35,989 --> 00:07:37,122
                    AAH!        

175
00:07:39,393 --> 00:07:41,293
                   PLEASE!      
                 TALK TO ME!    

176
00:07:43,430 --> 00:07:44,863
